{"tid":357702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［連登學術期刊發表］恭賀連登網民BillyLi（#115169）透過公投確認自己垃圾","createTime":"2017-08-13T06:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T23:50:40.000Z","uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8e0da8bca5703fc7fd406ad4c41d2b4588fe82bf","tid":357702,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T06:48:52.000Z","msg":"起源狂妄自大post <br />\n<br />\n讀 Mechanical Engineering有咩好發展?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/347347/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347347/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Highlight</span><br />\n-被眾人指出佢係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">垃圾</span></span>，佢極力否認，返指其人認為佢垃圾既都係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n-話話佢垃圾既人狂妄自大<br />\n<br />\n-無緣無故推論出話屌佢垃圾既人自以為好撚勁<br />\n<br />\n-HD2.98GPA稱為 有3 欺騙一眾網民，令人誤以為係3.3 3.6GPA 既有3<br />\n<br />\n-唔夠分入番ugc，無mtr ta interview 但堅持Mtr 唔in佢係唔明佢有無料<br />\n<br />\n-Poly Mech同一眾top up邊間比間有認受性都問唔自己google<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有見及此，為探討連登網民BillyLi讀書本質上是否客觀地垃圾，建議民調確認</span><br />\n<br />\n（比數至截稿前統計）<br />\n<br />\n1.佢自己民調以17:57大比數確認自己自己係垃圾<br />\n<br />\ndse入唔到u，hd讀engineering完左之後半工讀。咁樣係咪垃圾?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/355609/page/4?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/355609/page/4?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">-自發公投post確認自己垃圾</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">本人為證明佢垃圾係客觀，再用自己做替身公投多次。結果以超大比數2:32確認係垃圾，</span><br />\n<br />\n確認左佢既讀書上特點經公投確認為垃圾，而非針對佢本人本身<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[公投] DSE 失敗者 HD都入唔番u 報HD既工無回音 係咪垃圾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/356591/page/3?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/356591/page/3?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">分析民調</span></span><br />\n<br />\n本調查有兩個outcome<br />\n本身雙方既前設並無經特定方法證明，所以以公投方式以得較大支持基礎 <br />\n<br />\n1 -公投題目內容係客觀上垃圾，BillyLi離地缺乏社會認知<br />\n<br />\n2 -指BillyLi垃圾一方皆為離地垃圾自大<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兩次公投皆支持1既想法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總結</span></span><br />\n今次應該係有史以黎有網民以自發公投以證明自己垃圾。確立自己社會地位，雖然佢自己無乜感受，但呢個比較公正既民調可幫助佢日後發展成為成功人士<br />\n<br />\n調查有可取性，但未必100%確切反映社會觀點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝大家收睇 連登社會學既學術期刊發表<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">後話：因為自己做左替身，模擬網民思想回應其他人而遭受圍剿</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0406ccabe0b848ab8bdcc2549790e679fd8ecf7e","tid":357702,"uid":129825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T08:07:28.000Z","msg":"其實上連登點解要咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  成件事好好笑"},{"pid":"5552643913b744cd25a2e1fc45fdf62db444f709","tid":357702,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T23:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實上連登點解要咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  成件事好好笑</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}